name: PROPERTIES 01 - Hotel in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood. 
This property is strategically located in the downtown area of ​​Little Nostalgia, surrounded by restaurants, theaters and coffees that are part of the main charm and entertainment of Kitty City. 
Its construction of more than 90 years gives it an incomparable beauty in its 10 spacious rooms. 
Land measurements: 70m x 60
